# CSRD Phase 0 baseline sweep artifacts (audit §17.2 / phase-0-baseline.md §3.2)
# Keep the committed canonical baseline at docs/baselines/, but ignore the
# scratch directory the sweep writes per-scenario data and rolling logs into.
artifacts/tests/runs/baseline_v0/
artifacts/tests/runs/
artifacts/tests/generated_configs/

# Smoke baseline lives next to the canonical one but is regenerated on
# every run_all_tests('phase0') call; do not commit it.
docs/baselines/*.smoke.json
